{"tid":1488833,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"鄭若驊突然提早結束上海行程返港","createTime":"2019-08-19T17:04:45.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-19T17:41:31.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"5d10d1e91d1c4137bdc639411e65d0bf68f36b99","tid":1488833,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T17:04:45.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】律政司司長鄭若驊突然提早結束上海行程返港。<br />\n<br />\n鄭若驊凌晨十二時許在香港機場下機，未有回應記者提問，她的新聞秘書就指司長提早返港是要處理公務。<br />\n<br />\n鄭若驊是在周六前往上海，原定今天出席由律政司、上海市法學會、上海經貿商事調解中心合辦，主題為滬港商事調解研討會，並發表演說，之後才返香港，突然取消出席研討會，提早結束行程返港。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=359717\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D359717&d=3k3yiaJ8En3geZFfXz4NAFlsl4SrcEEyWLual4COuMU%3D&h=e2443b94\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D359717&h=9b4b3c4d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=359717</a>"},{"pid":"207714d068aad8dc41767af06298eb65e61aa6a5","tid":1488833,"uid":12662,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T17:06:01.000Z","msg":"關於噚晚馮競文喺灣仔籌錢第一身見證<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1488672\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1488672</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"220548f6e6b3868d392e05f0d1681c45f5c6e56f","tid":1488833,"uid":128569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T17:07:19.000Z","msg":"有咩事會咁急 係咪成班高官傾緊出老解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f59701619de278b88c598e5ac8e4ca76c067b82","tid":1488833,"uid":266172,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T17:07:56.000Z","msg":"收到信封？中共開完發up風會議，應該開始有動作。"},{"pid":"a46e0725180840b0cbe7067858933f1611e32e2e","tid":1488833,"uid":117276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-19T17:08:00.000Z","msg":"戒嚴未<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gi